</div>
<div class="container body-content">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 cell-frontpage full-width">
            <article>
                <header>
                    <h3><b>About me</b></h3>
                    <br>
                </header>
                <p align="justify">
                    My name is Nora Dimitrova and I am a lawyer.
                </p>
                <p align="justify">
                    During the period of working as an in-house lawyer I have provided legal services mainly
                    in the field of civil law and I was able to successfully develop good communicational and
                    organizational skills. I also had the opportunity to gain experience in teamwork, also participation
                    in international projects, banking and financial deals related to that projects, as well as preparation of
                    all type of legal documents and agreements, responding to the requirements and the nature of the work I performed.
                </p>
                <p align="justify">
                    I participated in the implementation of different projects, such as for the construction of a
                    Photovoltaic power plant, which project was funded by a large Italian bank, as well as
                    for the construction of cinema halls, as working on these projects helped me to improve my
                    managing skills, as well as to be responsible for the work I performed.
                </p>
                <p align="justify">
                    I provide legal services to legal entities as well as legal assistance to individuals, debt collection of banks and commercial companies, claim proceedings, bankruptcy and etc.
                </p>
                <p align="justify">
                    In my practice as a lawyer, I am convinced that the good and timely legal advice and
                    representation can reverse the course of each case.
                </p>
                <p align="justify">
                    I believe that the best results are always the result of mutual trust and cooperation between client and lawyer.
                </p>
                <footer>
                    <div class="pull-right">
                        <a class="btn btn-default btn-xs" href="/">Back &raquo;</a>
                    </div>
                </footer>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

